        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Securities Clarity Act </b></p> <p>This bill excludes an investment contract asset as being considered a security, including for disclosure and registration purposes. An investment contract asset as defined by the bill is a tangible or intangible asset sold pursuant to an investment contract that is not otherwise considered a security. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
